    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Requires the Public Utilities Commission to establish a streamlined grid-ready homes interconnection process.  Expands reporting requirements of the Hawaii Electricity Reliability Administrator to include reporting on the grid-ready home interconnection process.  Effective 7/1/3000.  (HD1)"
    }
